data.description: Welcome to a world of exquisite beauty and refined living at 17977 Carlton Dr. *Appraised value in November was $1,794,000 - now offered at 100K under appraised value! Nestled in a prestigious neighborhood, this home offers a harmonious blend of timeless elegance and cutting-edge amenities. This stately residence is a true architectural masterpiece, boasting a grand entrance, meticulous attention to detail, and ample opportunity for entertaining. The expansive living areas are designed with open concept living in mind. Abundant natural light, high ceilings, and stunning fixtures create a captivating atmosphere. The chef's kitchen is a culinary delight, featuring top-of-the-line appliances, a generous island, custom cabinetry, and a walk-in pantry - perfect for creating memorable meals. Enjoy lavish dinners in the formal dining room, where elegance and sophistication meet for an unforgettable dining experience. The home offers five bedrooms, each designed for ultimate comfort and relaxation. The master suite is a sanctuary with a spa-like en-suite bathroom. A dedicated media room, a game room, and a large wine closet with wet bar make this home the ultimate entertainment haven, perfect for hosting movie nights and celebrations. Located in a highly sought-after area of Edmond, this property offers the perfect balance of privacy and convenience. Excellent schools, shopping, dining, and major transportation routes are all within easy reach. 17977 Carlton Dr is a testament to the epitome of luxury living, offering impeccable design, world-class features, and a location that caters to those with discerning taste. Be sure to check out all the included upgrades on the Features & Amenities sheet. Don't miss the chance to own this extraordinary residence and live a life of opulence. Schedule a private tour today and experience the grandeur and comfort of this magnificent property – it's the dream home you've been waiting for!
